com.thomsonreuters.ema.access

Interface OmmArray

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.Collection<OmmArrayEntry>, Data, java.lang.Iterable<OmmArrayEntry>

    public interface OmmArray
extends Data, java.util.Collection<OmmArrayEntry>
    OmmArray is a homogeneous container of primitive data type entries.

    OmmArray is a collection which provides iterator over the elements in this collection.
